title: DGT Pursuing Tax Revenue Target (Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia)
text: ( Source : Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia ) Jakarta , 13/10/ 2015 MoF - As of 30 September 2015, realization of tax revenue reached IDR686.274 trillion or 53.02 percent of target set in Revised State Budget 2015 at IDR1,294.258
